t unto you, whosoever of you are justified by the law; ye are fallen from grace.","year":58},{"id":"recDCtcL3N8NYspXq","ref":"Gal.5.5","text":"For we through the Spirit wait for the hope of righteousness by faith.","year":58},{"id":"recErXw6ALvHNxzY8","ref":"Gal.5.6","text":"For in Jesus Christ neither circumcision availeth any thing, nor uncircumcision; but faith which worketh by love.","year":58},{"id":"recSJvl6ltNPuGIUD","ref":"Gal.5.7","text":"Ye did run well; who did hinder you that ye should not obey the truth?","year":58},{"id":"rec3bDtg0rRYCjgRk","ref":"Gal.5.8","text":"This persuasion cometh not of him that calleth you.","year":58}]}
